{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whoever survived it, survived it or not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think during the whole six weeks, if I got half an aspirin, then it's-- I didn't get anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was young, and I was not only six weeks away from home, from normal life, so I survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I survived it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many, many, many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in those six weeks, I made friends there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the meantime on the beginning, my family came to the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knocked on the window, and they could look in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then they didn't come anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I heard that they were taken away from Auschwitz to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I stayed there, in there six weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After six weeks, I was supposed to be released into-- back into the lager.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what shall I do now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody there, no friend, no relative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here, I know the people, and I am a nurse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, I would like to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were-- were there any doctors or any medical people in the barrack at all apart from you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I wasn't a medical.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just a nurse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were girls who looked after us, lying on the straw and bringing us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was actually much better than in the lager, because we had our straw bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got our food there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we don't have to stand every morning and every evening for that so-called [NON-ENGLISH], which was counting the heads for hours and hours in cold and in sun and everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same, the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, we were not so hungry anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The stomach somehow gets used to-- shrinks and gets used to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the beginning was the worst with the hunger.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
